---
title: sidecar_publishing (fulu-validator)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init : start
    q_init --> q_iter : for each data_column_sidecar in sidecars
    q_iter --> q_index : column_index = data_column_sidecar.index
    q_index --> q_subnet : subnet_id = compute_subnet_for_data_column_sidecar(column_index)
    q_subnet --> q_publish : publish sidecar to data_column_sidecar_{subnet_id} topic
    q_publish --> q_iter : next sidecar
    q_publish --> [*] : all sidecars published

    note right of q_subnet
        INV: Each sidecar is published to exactly one subnet
        INV: subnet_id is deterministically computed from column_index
        INV: All sidecars are published before completion
    end note
